<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <link href="/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="/js/handlebars.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-custom1 container-fluid p-0"> 
    
    <div class="header d-flex py-3 px-4 align-items-center">
        <a class="logo text-decoration-none text-reset fw-bold fs-4" href="#">{NULLPTR}</a>
        <div class="navbar-nav ms-auto d-flex flex-row gap-4">
            <a class="nav-link vacancies fw-bold text-dark text-decoration-none" href="#">ВСЕ ВАКАНСИИ</a>
            <a class="nav-link for-companies fw-bold text-dark text-decoration-none" href="#">ДЛЯ КОМПАНИЙ</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="border-top border-dark border-4 opacity-100 m-0">

    <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="row g-0">
            
            <div class="col-lg-8 hero-content py-5 px-5 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
                
                <h1 class="hero-title display-1 fw-bold text-uppercase lh-1 mb-4">
                    Пиши код.<br>
                    Не пиши<br>
                    <span class="text-danger">отписки.</span>
                </h1>
                
                <p class="hero-description fs-5 mb-5 w-75 text-secondary">
                    Платформа поиска работы для инженеров. Проверенные вакансии с прямыми контактами, открытыми вилками и прозрачным этапом отбора.
                </p>

                <div>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-danger rounded-0 border-0 px-5 py-3 fw-bold text-uppercase js-scroll-vacancies">
                        Смотреть вакансии
                    </a>
                </div>

            </div> 
            <div class="col-lg-4 hero-visual bg-dark d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center" style="min-height: 70vh;">
                <div class="display-1 text-danger fw-bold mb-4 lh-1">*</div>
                <code class="text-white fs-5">while(alive) { code(); }</code>
            </div> 
    </section>

    <hr class="border-top border-dark border-4 opacity-100 m-0">

    <section class="features-section">
        <div class="row g-0">
            
            <div class="col-lg-4 feature-card p-5 border-end border-dark border-4 bg-white">
                <div class="feature-number display-5 fw-bold mb-4">01</div>
                <h3 class="feature-title fs-4 fw-bold mb-3">Прямые контакты</h3>
                <p class="feature-description text-secondary mb-0">
                    Никаких HR-фильтров с вопросами "кем вы видите себя через 5 лет". Сразу общайтесь с техлидами и CTO.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4 feature-card p-5 border-end border-dark border-4 bg-white">
                <div class="feature-number display-5 fw-bold mb-4">02</div>
                <h3 class="feature-title fs-4 fw-bold mb-3">Открытые вилки</h3>
                <p class="feature-description text-secondary mb-0">
                    Зарплата известна до собеседования. Уважаем ваше время и не играем в угадайку на финальном оффере.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4 feature-card p-5 bg-white">
                <div class="feature-number display-5 fw-bold mb-4">03</div>
                <h3 class="feature-title fs-4 fw-bold mb-3">Строгий отбор компаний</h3>
                <p class="feature-description text-secondary mb-0">
                    В нашем списке нет галер. Только продуктовые команды, современные стеки и адекватные процессы.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="border-top border-dark border-4 opacity-100 m-0">

    <section class="jobs-section py-5 px-4 px-lg-5">
        
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-5">
            <h2 class="display-6 fw-bold mb-0 text-dark">Свежие вакансии</h2>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-dark rounded-0 border-2 px-4 py-2 fw-bold text-uppercase">
                Смотреть все
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4">
            
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="bg-white border border-dark border-2 p-4 h-100 d-flex flex-column text-decoration-none text-dark">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Senior Frontend Engineer</h4>
                    <div class="text-danger fw-bold fs-5 mb-2">350K - 450K ₽</div>
                    <div class="small text-dark fw-bold mb-4">
                        FinTech Core &bull; <span class="text-secondary fw-normal">Москва / Remote</span>
                    </div>
                    <hr class="border-dark opacity-100 mt-auto mb-3">
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="badge border border-dark text-dark bg-white rounded-0">REACT</span>
                        <span class="badge border border-dark text-dark bg-white rounded-0">TYPESCRIPT</span>
                        <span class="badge border border-dark text-dark bg-white rounded-0">FSD</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="bg-white border border-dark border-2 p-4 h-100 d-flex flex-column text-decoration-none text-dark">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Go Backend Developer</h4>
                    <div class="text-danger fw-bold fs-5 mb-2">€4000 - €6000</div>
                    <div class="small text-dark fw-bold mb-4">
                        StreamData &bull; <span class="text-secondary fw-normal">Remote</span>
                    </div>
                    <hr class="border-dark opacity-100 mt-auto mb-3">
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="badge border border-dark text-dark bg-white rounded-0">GOLANG</span>
                        <span class="badge border border-dark text-dark bg-white rounded-0">POSTGRESQL</span>
                        <span class="badge border border-dark text-dark bg-white rounded-0">KAFKA</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="bg-white border border-dark border-2 p-4 h-100 d-flex flex-column text-decoration-none text-dark">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Lead DevOps / SRE</h4>
                    <div class="text-danger fw-bold fs-5 mb-2">ОТ 400 000 ₽</div>
                    <div class="small text-dark fw-bold mb-4">
                        CloudNexus &bull; <span class="text-secondary fw-normal">Санкт-Петербург / Office</span>
                    </div>
                    <hr class="border-dark opacity-100 mt-auto mb-3">
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="badge border border-dark text-dark bg-white rounded-0">TERRAFORM</span>
                        <span class="badge border border-dark text-dark bg-white rounded-0">ANSIBLE</span>
                        <span class="badge border border-dark text-dark bg-white rounded-0">AWS</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="border-top border-dark border-4 opacity-100 m-0">

</body>
</html>